description:
Progress through the story by solving the appropriate puzzles, and cute girls will keep you company! The game has a variety of puzzles that will make you show all the skills of mindfulness and logic. And beautiful girls will surely reward you for your efforts.

The mechanics of the game is simple, but the difficulty of the puzzles increases as you progress. Yes, and their beautiful outfit can distract you... so maybe help them get rid of it? Every success on your part will make them happier.

All images opened during the game are saved in a separate gallery, where you can always return and look at the fruits of your labors!

Key features:
• Excellent workout for the mind and logic;
• Lots of levels with different difficulty;
• Several types of different puzzles;
• Lovely girls will not leave you indifferent;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;
• Relaxing musical accompaniment;
